<Content>Don't Miss the Hilton Florence Metropole This truly excellent property is the best value in Italy. Two-years-new, the hotel rooms have a modern decor and are spacious, comfortable, and sparkling clean. The staff, including the business manager live to meet your every need. Pay a few dollars extra for a room that gives you access to the excutive lounge and spa. You won't be disappointed. The executive lounge provides an unbelievable breakfast and so much good food during the day/evening that you'll never go hungry. The jacuzzi pool in the spa is a once-in-a-lifetime experience. The hotel is located on the outskirts of Florence and provides bus/van service to city-center. This allows you to experience all of the tourist sites in Florence and still feel like you're sleeping in the Tuscany countryside. If I had it to do over, I would have stayed at this hotel for both the Florence and the Rome part of our vacation. You can take a train or tour bus to Rome for day trips. 
